Kingdom Street.name: Kingdom Street

Tavern.name: Tavern
Tavern.description: This is the only tavern in Viridis.

Tavern.description: Volunteers, adventurers and soldiers are meeting in the tavern to organize and talk about adventures they lived through. Currently more and more goblins are gathering here. Hopefully they stay peaceful.
Tavern.name: Tavern

Marketplace.description: There is a lot of hustle and bustle on the market square. Numerous adventurers offer their hard-earned wares here.
Marketplace.name: Marketplace

Arena.name: Arena
Arena.description: This is the arena of Viridis.

Blacksmith Shop.description: Adventurers gathered here for weapons and armors.
Blacksmith Shop.name: Blacksmith Shop

Stable.description: Adventurers gathered here for mounts, such as deers.
Stable.name: Stable

Gate of Viridis.description: You see an opened metal gate in front of you. Guards are patrolling on the city walls...
Gate of Viridis.name: Gate of Viridis

Border of Slime Forest.description: You are about to enter the famous slime forest!
Border of Slime Forest.name: Border of Slime Forest

A Lake in Slime Forest.description: You see a beautiful lake here.
A Lake in Slime Forest.name: A Lake in Slime Forest

Deep Slime Forest.description: You can smell dangerous creatures hiding in the deep forest...
Deep Slime Forest.name: Deep Slime Forest

4157328219.description: The is a trail to the goblin village. Some goblin kids are playing here.
4157328219.name: A Small Trail in Forest

1890697340.description: Goblins collect stones and built a small village here. Goblin farmers and slaves come and go.
1890697340.name: Goblin Village

1076912521.description: Goblins farmers are "farming" in this place. Human, elf, and the other species are caught, tied and served as food storage for goblins.
1076912521.name: Goblin Farm

3261122532.description: This trail toward the Goblin Stronghold, you can smell danger here.
3261122532.name: A Trail to Goblin Stronghold

3993644110.description: Goblins use logs and stones to construct this stronghold. Numerous goblin warriors and archers are patrolling here.
3993644110.name: Gate of Goblin Stronghold

3928306209.description: You see several barracks inside the stronghold, and many goblin soldiers are here to train their fighting skills.
3928306209.name: Goblin Barracks

1308733309.description: Several hunters setup a hut and take rest in this place. Adventurers are using this place as a hideout before going further to Goblin Stronghold
1308733309.name: Hunter's Hut

3990661765.description: It is hard to imagine that how goblins built such a huge structure with cracked stones and wood logs. You noticed that there are many humanoid species confined in wood cages here, without proper keys, you are unable to unlock and release these poor souls.
3990661765.name: Goblin Stronghold

1685188295.description: An opening leads into the rock. As you go in further you hear a flappy Noise.
1685188295.name: A Cave Entry in Deep Slime Forest

1255834052.description: it get's darker around you. You can only see a faint light reaching from the entry of the cave. The cave makes a turn to west direction.
1255834052.name: Deep Slime Forest Cave

1827556448.description:
You cannot see the entry anymore. Someone has fixed a torch to the stone here. Without the torch it would be pitchblack here and you couldn't see anything here.
But wait? Where does the torch come from? Was somebody in here before you? Why does the Torch still burn?

Opposite side of the torch you can see carved letters in the stone. 
It reads - Array(16).join("wat" - 1)
1827556448.name: Deep Slime Forest Cave

3157652150.description:
The arena of Viridis is a circle formed sand place surrounded by rows of stacked stone steps.
The arena is about 20 Meters in diameter while the whole arena with the places for the audience is about 70 Meters in diameter.

Soldiers and Adventurers train and show there fighting skills there. Sometimes the crazy Monster Hunter brings some new creatures he found on his travels, that the Volunteers can examine them and test their skills on them
3157652150.name: Arena of Viridis

1532924546.name: A Path to the Mountains

3031060375.description: You are standing on the north trail of Mordesh Mountains, an highland area with bare soil and few low growth plants.
3031060375.name: North of Mordesh

1344362146.description: This is a highland area with bare soil and few low growth plants. Creatures living here are survivalists, and they became aggressive and strong. You can hear noises come from the west.
1344362146.name: Mordesh Highland

1582888825.description: You are standing in front of the Bronze Tribe, which is the oldest orc tribe in Mordesh Highland. These orcs are well-known for their aggression to human, so be careful!
1582888825.name: Gate of Bronze Tribe

1987763122.description: Orcs of Bronze Tribe are well-known for their aggression to human. These orcs like to two things, axes and heads, especially the heads of human.
1987763122.name: Bronze Tribe

308461798.description: Old Kingdom Road is directed to the palace. The queen of Chiania Kingdom wants to see flowers and trees from her palace, so she hired hundreds of workers and gardeners to renovate this road. Now people call this place "Garden Road".

3056209586.description: You are standing on the southern road of Viridis, this place is bustling with people.
3056209586.name: Port Access Street

1673099053.description: Large ships are berthed in the distance, laborers are busy moving goods. Everyone here is busy getting on with the business of the day. A few shady men keep a lookout near the corner. The harbor master's office is closed.
1673099053.name: Port of Viridis

1472782334.description: The wooden planks under your feet are solid, the birds squawk awaiting their next meal. Large ships being loaded on either side of you keep the sea out of sight.
1472782334.name: Docks of Viridis

1135490743.description: A large iron gate is bosomed between stone walls, the town guards stand near alert to all that approach. A well worn path leads down to the beach.
1135490743.name: Waterfront Gate

2923643023.description: The path from town turns from soil to sand, the sea goes beyond the horizon as long grasses sway along beach. Formidable crabs are patrolling the sea for their next meal between the debris that has washed ashore.
2923643023.name: Windswept Beach - North

402139840.description: Eroded and unusable paths dot the impenetrable cliffs that keep the ocean at bay. Crabs with pincers as large as you've ever seen squabble over the rights to prime real estate. A group of walruses is sunning on their stretch while the large bull keeps a lookout.
402139840.name: Windswept Beach

676993241.description: The sand dead ends as the cliffs approach the sea. The mast of an ancient ship wreck can be seen just above the waves in the distance. A cave in the cliff comes into view, the smell of smoke emanates from it's opening and it gives you a feeling of unease.
676993241.name: Windswept Beach - South

Cliffside Cave Entrance.description: Discarded decaying clothing and broken crab carapaces litter the ground. The cave goes deeper but it's too dark to tell how far.
Cliffside Cave Entrance.name: Cliffside Cave Entrance

3092719748.description: Barrels and boxes are stacked against a wall. Thousands of carved lines decorate the walls. You see the cave split into two tunnels.
3092719748.name: Cliffside Lair

1578118356.description: Only large enough for one well equipped man the tunnel winds higher through the rock. Small outcroppings and the creatures that lurk in them come out of nowhere.
1578118356.name: Cliffside Lair Small Tunnel

4209750828.description: The tunnel is small but not impassable, sharp rocks remind you to watch your step. A mysterious tunnel and a wretched smell is the only notable thing around.
4209750828.name: Cliffside Lair Small Tunnel Connector

765767385.description: You can see nothing, the stench tells you what's here, the clang of cutlery tells you where it's at.
765767385.name: Cliffside Lair Dark Tunnel

2049168772.description: A great cavern appears below the rock balcony in which you stand. Rusted swords litter the perimeter.
2049168772.name: Cliffside Lair Overlook

2512262248.description: The cave opens up into a large cavern, a fire is lit near what appears to be a make shift stage with a wooden table. Bones fresh and old lie in a pile.
2512262248.name: Cliffside Lair Great Cavern

Down Staircase.name: Down Staircase
Down Staircase.listen: You can hear noises from... unknown monsters...
